{
  "stem": "7938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he wanted to correct a misrepresentation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was written, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Keneally in his book mentioned that it was for money manipulations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which was a-- which was not the right thing which was happened to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he explained it to me from A to Z exactly what had happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was, as far as his character was, he was 100% He was not a rich man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't request any money, he didn't take any money, any penny from this, because everything was in the books.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't take anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the money to the Germans except--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--or the rest which was remaining, which people needed for moving people around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For keeping hospitals, for keeping everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the jail, he came out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After 18 months, he came out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was in '41 already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they initiated another trial that it was-- that he dealt-- the [GERMAN] started this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That he was not supposed to have money, the Jews are not supposed to have money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they started this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a professor of the university who was-- who defended him in this trial, and he was acquitted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he came back to the ghetto, and he lived in the ghetto a couple of two or three months, and he died.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we went outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my father couldn't get any permission to go to ghetto, because he was already 60 years old, or almost 60.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we took-- we were in the suburbs of Cracow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a sp-- a village, Borek Falecki.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how they called it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived there, from-- we had to move there right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, in '40.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Actually, we moved there in '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
